<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201124/8d98563680d74cafb4f50bdc49d2e49f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>CHARACTER INTRODUCTION</p>
<p><strong>陈向军</strong></p>
<p>主治医师</p>
